utils
=====

Table of Contents
=================

make-libraries-doc
	Generates documentation about the PHPLint Library (modules + stdlib).
	Usage: ./make-libraries-doc

make-pure-c-version
	Builds the pure-c version of the distributable PHPLint package.
	Used by Makefile.

make-tokens-module
	Builds src/Tokens.imp module that maps symbols into strings.
	Defined symbols are read from src/Scanner.def.
	Used by Makefile.
